// ── ARTIST NORMALIZATION ──────────────────────────────────────
// Rules:
//   - Strip leading symbols/brackets/quotes/spaces
//   - Strip zero-padded track prefixes (0, 01, 09, 001 … always start with 0)
//   - Keep bare single/multi non-zero digits ("2 Brothers", "1 Alarma", "10cc")
